Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光、龙咲海、凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被艾美诺公主召唤成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救异世界锡菲罗的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻惑士卡尔汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令假的艾美诺公主出现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击光等人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N海逃出了那个巧妙的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她击伤卡尔汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令阿斯克特改邪归正
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 光等人继续旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前去找寻第二部魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样你也不在乎吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界上最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气死人了 对着那种丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然个个都一败涂地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真失败
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 就由我这个国色天香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身材玲珑浮凸的卡尔汀娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜!\N别再伤害魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗 阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果收拾了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能得到谢加图的巨额奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本不需要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 别管魔法骑士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特 你好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当你是我的亲弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你就能一生一世地快乐生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:03:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我一定会打倒魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿 究竟还要走多久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才去到那座\N浮在半空的山啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要爬过多少座那种山啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是那样说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有四座吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你高兴什么!莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一开始就不喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那副毫无紧张感的笑容!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而战斗时\N你为何总是不知所踪啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会喜欢\N偷偷看着我们受苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!我一定要弄明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那个软绵绵\N的身体内有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要走!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!莫歌拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能去到那座岩山吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二部魔神在沉睡的那座岩山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力赶路 一定能到达的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要快点得到第二部魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 小海 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以等一下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到些声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是女人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…\N没打算和蝙蝠先生加深认识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人会好危险!等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以去那边!小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很粗鲁的招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见这么美艳动人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么粗鲁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!这不是大阪口音吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗的语言系统里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也包括了大阪口音吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这里也有大阪呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫卡尔汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位小姐的名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何这种时候\N要自我介绍啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫狮堂光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙咲海呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光?龙咲海?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怪的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思呢!我们要去找小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无时间奉陪你这个大阪怪女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一位小姐原来叫小风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风迷了路全因你的关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的事 你们不用担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事你为何知道啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上会让你们见面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么天真感谢我\N我不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谢加图的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以听铃声…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜!卡尔汀娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那边!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那边呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:09:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 小海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 小海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 小海 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里会有强风吹过 好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 小海 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何要袭击我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐你真擅长躲避啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐你真擅长躲避啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不出来的话始终不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是舞娘卡尔汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也懂这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些蝙蝠…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道小光\N和小海也…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们两个已经只会听命于我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是谢加图的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我打倒你们魔法骑士…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能赚一大笔钱呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是收了钱就会交足货的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专业舞娘兼幻惑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我和你们无仇无怨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彬彬有礼的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何一直不拔剑反击!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光和小海是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在锡菲罗只有三个的宝贵同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不能伤害她们!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满口漂亮话!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你也避得过吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…怎么办才好!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在锡菲罗这里\N—切都取决于心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有信念的心的力量\N足以决定未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来 你从心底相信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别犹疑!风!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有信念的心的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惩罚之风!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是将会成为\N魔法骑士的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是小看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你拔剑是个错误!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众少 有点冷清 但没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始下一场表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…自己…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反抗是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能抵挡我的幻术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制别人的感觉真好\N我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然传说的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个了不起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些可爱的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也不外如是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小光!醒来!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下次真的\N会令你们受重伤的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不!我或许会杀死你们!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士不是坏人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别妨碍我!静静地看着!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人不是你的同伴吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特就像我弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那么重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何要这么过份!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特还是个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让他细小的手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你们魔法骑士的血玷污
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候完结了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后就用魔法了结她们吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光和小海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我宝贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贵的…同伴!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐你马上\N也会跟她们上路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量…\N有信念的心的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来…足以决定未来!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死她们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚… 不可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…疾风!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么!?我不明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为锡菲罗第一幻惑士的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何会输给你们这种小姐!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:18:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的确比我强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你为了钱要杀我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那会令你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己的性命也豁出去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有理由会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的性命只是我自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果为了小光和小海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像可以豁出性命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你的幻术\N迷惑伤害她们两人时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想用自己拥有的一切力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救她们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想豁出性命拯救宝贵的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豁出性命?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们很久以前起已是朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 在由东京被召唤来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个异世界锡菲罗之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们根本不知道有对方的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何在那么短的时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以为她们豁出性命?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心是不可用时间来衡量的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起的时间多短暂也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对她们还有许多不了解也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了和她们一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特先生也和我一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他拼死保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜!\N别再伤害魔法骑士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你豁出性命想拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜小姐和我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比不上小姐你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有人能令自己豁出性命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是好是坏很难有一个准则
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我好佩服你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少 比起不知为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引起这次骚动的谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你更能打动我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神官谢加图的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是支配锡菲罗这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不能使用祈祷的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种不安定充满魔物的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支配了也没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也问过他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其让锡菲罗这么混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如叫艾美诺公主继续祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后由他全权\N支配这世界更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那位帅哥笑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说 [有东西比锡菲罗更重要]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比锡菲罗更重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我怎样问他\N他都没回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有什么重大内情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是时候走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去城堡吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再回去那种地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是谢加图的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你放心吧 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:21:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她是阿斯克特\N挺身保护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们帮不到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你们要努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图非常厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会说再见啊 阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 我们马上能再见面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们走远了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 莫歌拿先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何要感谢战斗时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是逃跑的家伙啊?小风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它秘密地\N拿了什么法宝出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它好像说不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:21:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比锡菲罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比锡菲罗…更重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:10.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,海的颜色逐渐染成红色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想就此被风带走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以不认输的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过经常跳不过的栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但用不完的实力是谁所赐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心底不褪色的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,背着阳光透出耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:38.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,面带最美的笑容用力踏脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:45.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,逆风也不可以沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:51.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不输给悲伤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:58.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:23:03.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着广阔海洋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:10.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你的瞳孔终有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:16.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会在阳光下散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:23.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:28.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念化成奔向明日的勇气
